{"tid":2463620,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《關於地球的運動》第6話","createTime":"2021-03-27T00:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T05:51:04.000Z","uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"747a061e16ba4f45a1340ca14cd75376c1ff23d7","tid":2463620,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:24:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mangabz.com/m168451/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mangabz.com%2Fm168451%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWmqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=48818480\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mangabz.com/m168451/</a><br />\n<br />\n故事背景簡介：故事以15世紀的歐洲作為背景，羅馬天主教以外，或者質疑上帝創世論都會被當作異端思想，不斷被處以火刑的時代。主角神童拉法爾已經預定好了要跳級上大學，而大家也都期待他去專攻當時最為重要的神學。對於最為重視合理性的拉法爾而言這是必然的選擇，只要遵循合理性世界就是易如反掌的。然而某一天，在拉法爾的身邊出現的神秘男人，他所研究的正是在異端思想中最核心的「真理」，地動說。<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPPVeLTF5P4rvwj7PqcJVZv1wDazWVH7dNCHjJe1pB73s?filename=kCsDrWS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCsDrWS.jpg&h=9c7f492f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTmufDxZonAitzsRY2TEAcfUHKnMN2i2mqgWPcbn3txVV?filename=AgXG9ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgXG9ad.jpg&h=b4d3cc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeFEd3CVp5fMa8WzR5CPiTT6dn6ezF6tCZpy8Ky9DPdw3?filename=xy1s4Jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxy1s4Jz.jpg&h=4e9107dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e11608eefd70e6272e4cae66c238b594320b9eca","tid":2463620,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9b3e3554edde805dc9880895979de6c609412b","tid":2463620,"uid":381265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"Dr.Stone開托左教科書既出路"},{"pid":"9fa49998e5101fb62e8f453e04adcb51c94d0d06","tid":2463620,"uid":309398,"like":0,"d